    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/ask/34591">原文</a><br/>
列出可用的ruby版本以安装类型：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm list known</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>然后从已知的列表中安装，输入：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm install VERSION_NUMBER</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>然后使用你已经安装的ruby版本：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm use VERSION_NUMBER</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>你可以使一个特定的ruby版本成为你的默认系统版本：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm use VERSION_NUMBER --default</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>要删除gem版本，保持gemsets：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm uninstall VERSION_NUMBER</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>删除ruby等：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm remove VERSION_NUMBER</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>要了解你的ruby环境以及它们的安装位置/别名：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm info</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
